ÅVariable-typeÄ


InGFA-Basicweusetheexpressions'byte','word'and'integer'forthe
threeinteger-variables(postfixes'|','&'and'%').Becauseallthree
areintegers,theexpression'integer'forthe4-byteinteger-variableis
