   NEXTi


ÅTIME$Ä


YoucanuseTIME$toprintthecurrenttimeonthescreen.Inthe
ProcedureClockyou'llfindawaytoprintthetimeeverysecond,although
TIME$isupdatedeveryàtwoÄseconds:

